text: == Events == * Great Conspiracy: Picts, Scotti and Saxons reach Londinium and plunder the city. * An earthquake strikes Nicaea (Turkey). == Births == * Eustochium, Desert Mother and saint * Juqu Mengxun, prince of the Xiongnu state Northern Liang * Philostorgius, Anomoean church historian == Deaths == * Caesarius of Nazianzus, physician and politician * Hilary of Poitiers, bishop and Doctor of the Church Category:360s
